,"original_language":"en"},{"id":3009,"adult":false,"title":"The Trial","video":false,"overview":"Arrested for an unnamed crime, Josef K. is trapped in a surreal bureaucratic maze where justice is unknowable and guilt is assumed.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":1.6207,"vote_count":543,"poster_path":"/4qDUe5HqB8pXNplSBlsoyVjNP3r.jpg","release_date":"1962-08-25","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/yhfHeIsR5Ki02b5SqBuLqAsLDCk.jpg","original_title":"Le Procès","original_language":"en"},{"id":657838,"adult":false,"title":"The Pity of War","video":false,"overview":"Professor Niall Ferguson argues that Britain's decision to enter the First World War was a catastrophic error that unleashed an era of totalitarianism and genocide.","genre_ids":[99,36,10752],"popularity":0.2464,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/55369ITmdPV6183crZw6yPnweed.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-28","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/93pXekK9jQTmCCbM2rNePMXhKKi.jpg","original_title":"The Pity of War","original_language":"en"},{"id":6961,"adult":false,"title":"The Wedding Date","video":false,"overview":"With the wedding of her younger sister fast approaching, Kat Ellis faces the undesirable prospect of traveling alone to London for the ceremony. While this is bad enough, Jeffrey, the man who left her as they moved closer to marriage, happens to be the groom's best man. Determined to show everyone -- most of all Jeffrey -- that her romantic life is as full and thrilling as ever, Kat hires a charming male escort as her date.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":1.9276,"vote_count":1239,"poster_path":"/t0AEzycJ6V8dLVlSudCUAA9mzgn.jpg","release_date":"2005-02-04","vote_average":6.819,"backdrop_path":"/wi8y24BI9sa8XSnH9vFmmYin6Km.jpg","original_title":"The Wedding Date","original_language":"en"},{"id":612,"adult":false,"title":"Munich","video":false,"overview":"During the 1972 Olympic Games in Munich, eleven Israeli athletes are taken hostage and murdered by a Palestinian terrorist group known as Black September. In retaliation, the Israeli government recruits a group of Mossad agents to track down and execute those responsible for the attack.","genre_ids":[18,28,36,53],"popularity":3.3549,"vote_count":2917,"poster_path":"/iUekaw96QLInZpsNwRTlRKrZgwm.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-23","vote_average":7.137,"backdrop_path":"/titl6uMe5u974sLAA2Zy1kFi4sC.jpg","original_title":"Munich","original_language":"en"},{"id":628,"adult":false,"title":"Interview with the Vampire","video":false,"overview":"A vampire relates his epic life story of love, betrayal, loneliness, and dark hunger to an over-curious reporter.","genre_ids":[27,18,14],"popularity":6.4796,"vote_count":6310,"poster_path":"/2162lAT2MP36MyJd2sttmj5du5T.jpg","release_date":"1994-11-11","vote_average":7.385,"backdrop_path":"/3fChciF2G1wXHsyTfJD9y7uN6Il.jpg","original_title":"Interview with the Vampire","original_language":"en"},{"id":634,"adult":false,"title":"Bridget Jones's Diary","video":false,"overview":"Bridget Jones is an average woman struggling against expectations. As a New Year's resolution, Bridget decides to take control of her life, starting by keeping a diary in which she will always tell the complete truth. Her charming boss takes an interest in her, and she cannot stop running into a rather disagreeable acquaintance whom Bridget cannot help finding quietly attractive.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18],"popularity":5.3605,"vote_count":5415,"poster_path":"/dkauRl9TosBFikftrC3OVcKWDoz.jpg","release_date":"2001-04-13","vote_average":6.74,"backdrop_path":"/9rSpxsMhG1FnFtUDdvSAXdtLtb3.jpg","original_title":"Bridget Jones's Diary","original_language":"en"},{"id":542,"adult":false,"title":"The Crime of Padre Amaro","video":false,"overview":"Sent to Mexico to help take care of aging Father Benito, young Father Amaro faces a moral challenge when he meets a 16-year-old girl who he starts an affair with. Likewise, the girl's mother had been having an affair with Father Benito. Father Amaro must choose between a holy or